    "No statistically significant difference was observed between the lower predicted treatment effect subgroup, 0.091 (95% CI: -0.231 to 0.413), and the higher predicted treatment effect subgroup, 0.070 (95% CI: -0.243 to 0.383) (P > 0.05).",
